1. Correct my grammar, spelling, word-choices, phrasings, conjugations, etc. to make my translation sound correct, like a native speaker's. Display your corrections by showing my translation, with the errors crossed out and your additions in bold.
2. Rate my translation out of 100
3. If you see me make the same mistake multiple times, point it out as something I should focus on improving
4. Offer your own translation, independent of whatever I wrote.

